EurotaxGlass,is,a,leading,provider,of,data,solutions,and,business,intelligence,services,for,the,European,automotive,community,They,provide,the,Valuation,API,which,enables,users,to,determine,the,value,of,a,car,based,on,information,such,as,the,country,in,which,the,vehicle,is,located,its,condition,and,its,mileage,This,service,is,programmatically,accessible,using,SOAP,calls,issued,in,XML,format